      "text": "JavaAPI通过线程枚举Thread.State区分的状态",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "eB6ghyynTwfzHrAgJBb3O",
      "originalText": "JavaAPI通过线程枚举Thread.State区分的状态",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "eT_LiQgpY6YVei3VM0HN_",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1493.1608542448423,
      "y": 3930.7737166117417,
      "width": 794.86376953125,
      "height": 40,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCPy",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1389575995,
      "version": 38,
      "versionNonce": 220557200,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "线程通过方法来进行判断是否被中断，也可以调用静态方法来进行判断当前线程是否被中断，不过\nThread.interrupted()会同时将中断标识位改写为false。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "线程通过方法来进行判断是否被中断，也可以调用静态方法来进行判断当前线程是否被中断，不过Thread.interrupted()会同时将中断标识位改写为false。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
