      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "FutureTask类实现了RunnableFuture接口，RunnableFuture继承了Runnable接口和Future接口，而\nFutureTask实现了RunnableFuture接口。所以它既可以作为Runnable被线程执行，又可以作为Future得到\nCallable的返回值。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "KulNmxU7eRkZDy5WeKAAX",
      "originalText": "FutureTask类实现了RunnableFuture接口，RunnableFuture继承了Runnable接口和Future接口，而FutureTask实现了RunnableFuture接口。所以它既可以作为Runnable被线程执行，又可以作为Future得到Callable的返回值。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
