      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "join&get\njoin()和get()方法都是用来获取CompletableFuture异步之后的返回值。。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "join&get\njoin()和get()方法都是用来获取CompletableFuture异步之后的返回值。。",
