    },
    {
      "id": "uLBqlq_kDrwPcLFHLJGDb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -58.190010293525916,
      "y": 4187.908368590705,
      "width": 619.0151163736977,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#f8f9fa",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCWv",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 952206357,
      "version": 373,
      "versionNonce": 917417840,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "避免嵌套回调‌：与直接嵌套 thenApply 不同，thenCompose 通过返回\nCompletionStage 直接扁平化异步链，减少嵌套层级，提升代码可读\n性。例如：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "避免嵌套回调‌：与直接嵌套 thenApply 不同，thenCompose 通过返回 CompletionStage 直接扁平化异步链，减少嵌套层级，提升代码可读性。例如：",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "MaMLcoynrUfatBtAEl9IP",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3008.3487452963163,
      "y": 4296.281476500864,
      "width": 1437.7012939453123,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#f8f9fa",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCWw",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1097800789,
      "version": 530,
      "versionNonce": 1416249232,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "thenApply转换的是泛型中的类型，并返回一个新的封装了转换结果的CompletableFuture实例；\nthenCompose 将内部的 CompletableFuture 调用展开来并使用上一个CompletableFutre 调用的结果在下一步的 CompletableFuture 调用中进行运算，是生成一个\n新的CompletableFuture。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "thenApply转换的是泛型中的类型，并返回一个新的封装了转换结果的CompletableFuture实例；\nthenCompose 将内部的 CompletableFuture 调用展开来并使用上一个CompletableFutre 调用的结果在下一步的 CompletableFuture 调用中进行运算，是生成一个新的CompletableFuture。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
