      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "默认情况下 CompletableFuture 会使用公共的 ForkJoinPool 线程池",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "B0TFzSeDkWUvi1SPIuquW",
      "originalText": "默认情况下 CompletableFuture 会使用公共的 ForkJoinPool 线程池",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "G-31PeYeR_51akDOKtgAY",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -6150.603326226185,
      "y": 2062.681660017305,
      "width": 860.629720052083,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Ck7smgeqvEVFuTCo53UeW"
      ],
      "frameId": "6UhhB8zWpRnyjFzvSf06g",
      "index": "cCcR",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 873441045,
      "version": 363,
      "versionNonce": 299922800,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "aFbGM9olLSEupa8AH-wer",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -6145.603326226185,
      "y": 2067.681660017305,
      "width": 841.459228515625,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Ck7smgeqvEVFuTCo53UeW"
      ],
      "frameId": "6UhhB8zWpRnyjFzvSf06g",
      "index": "cCcS",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 966470357,
      "version": 364,
      "versionNonce": 1386207632,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "这个线程池默认创建的线程数是 CPU 的核数（也可以通过 JVM option:-\nDjava.util.concurrent.ForkJoinPool.common.parallelism 来设置 ForkJoinPool 线程池的线程数）",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "G-31PeYeR_51akDOKtgAY",
      "originalText": "这个线程池默认创建的线程数是 CPU 的核数（也可以通过 JVM option:-Djava.util.concurrent.ForkJoinPool.common.parallelism 来设置 ForkJoinPool 线程池的线程数）",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "VnkyHXL8YkPR9yXMBKr-J",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -6150.603326226185,
      "y": 2127.7433959475716,
      "width": 991,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Ck7smgeqvEVFuTCo53UeW"
      ],
      "frameId": "6UhhB8zWpRnyjFzvSf06g",
      "index": "cCcT",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 2145198901,
      "version": 313,
      "versionNonce": 185616240,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "IRvNJNCAduDVc1xRIA-UK",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -6145.603326226185,
      "y": 2132.7433959475716,
      "width": 961.2197265625,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Ck7smgeqvEVFuTCo53UeW"
      ],
      "frameId": "6UhhB8zWpRnyjFzvSf06g",
      "index": "cCcU",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1769925179,
      "version": 386,
      "versionNonce": 579741584,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "如果所有 CompletableFuture 共享一个线程池，那么一旦有任务执行一些很慢的 I/O 操作，就会导致线程池中\n所有线程都阻塞在 I/O 操作上，从而造成线程饥饿，进而影响整个系统的性能",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "VnkyHXL8YkPR9yXMBKr-J",
      "originalText": "如果所有 CompletableFuture 共享一个线程池，那么一旦有任务执行一些很慢的 I/O 操作，就会导致线程池中所有线程都阻塞在 I/O 操作上，从而造成线程饥饿，进而影响整个系统的性能",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "-q_ly4TLBa2XB75sz9cJg",
      "type": "rectangle",
