      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "这种变量在多线程环境下访问（通过get和set方法访问）时能保证各个线程的变量相对独立于其他线程内的变量",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "这种变量在多线程环境下访问（通过get和set方法访问）时能保证各个线程的变量相对独立于其他线程内的变量",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "8IurOi_yI2_uJEcknpoA2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1872.2378060751403,
      "y": 3640.1141217856402,
      "width": 708.7197265625,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
