      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ThreadLocal实例通常来说都是private static类型的，用于关联线程和线程上下文",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ThreadLocal实例通常来说都是private static类型的，用于关联线程和线程上下文",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "uRTsDi61monmwVeg-rVdF",
