      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ThreadLocal的优势",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ThreadLocal的优势",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "0qHCVD6DhVUXBy9qIOyaf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2829.445584102641,
      "y": 4456.541998607278,
      "width": 472.4198913574219,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCco",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1581433749,
      "version": 87,
      "versionNonce": 1229779856,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "在一些特定场景下，ThreadLocal有两个突出的优势：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "在一些特定场景下，ThreadLocal有两个突出的优势：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "zJotYWUQmtMeZILy4tXpV",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3063.7656391038026,
      "y": 4515.062019088817,
      "width": 963.2261678099222,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCcp",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 787262523,
      "version": 131,
      "versionNonce": 1960430960,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1.传递数据 ： 保存每个线程绑定的数据，在需要的地方可以直接获取, 避免参数直接传递带来的代码耦合问题",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1.传递数据 ： 保存每个线程绑定的数据，在需要的地方可以直接获取, 避免参数直接传递带来的代码耦合问题",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "T-I-N4QcQeeOxNQKGYmt7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3061.5964379862467,
      "y": 4551.541998607279,
      "width": 787.0999755859375,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCcq",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 78612725,
      "version": 89,
      "versionNonce": 948437392,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2.线程隔离 ： 各线程之间的数据相互隔离却又具备并发性，避免同步方式带来的性能损失",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2.线程隔离 ： 各线程之间的数据相互隔离却又具备并发性，避免同步方式带来的性能损失",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
