      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Spring的事务就借助了ThreadLocal类。Spring会从数据库连接池中获得一个\nconnection，然会把connection放进ThreadLocal中，也就和线程绑定了，事务需要提交\n或者回滚，只要从ThreadLocal中拿到connection进行操作。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Spring的事务就借助了ThreadLocal类。Spring会从数据库连接池中获得一个connection，然会把connection放进ThreadLocal中，也就和线程绑定了，事务需要提交或者回滚，只要从ThreadLocal中拿到connection进行操作。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "chcFOKc7j02LeosInNJJd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1982.8234446680237,
      "y": 5522.839220340582,
      "width": 620,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCd9",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2139515291,
      "version": 39,
      "versionNonce": 1620885872,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "​这个设计与我们一开始说的设计刚好相反，这样设计有如下两个优势：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "​这个设计与我们一开始说的设计刚好相反，这样设计有如下两个优势：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "53sT-wHIAMgZf2m0rBjU-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1912.5045729588292,
      "y": 5458.124346720891,
      "width": 297.219970703125,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCdA",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1263099797,
      "version": 143,
      "versionNonce": 362696080,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "除了构造方法之外， 有以下4个：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "除了构造方法之外， 有以下4个：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "aMMsVH5XkkIrP-uPoKG6_",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -1989.7817630808058,
      "y": 5617.011038443636,
      "width": 459,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#f783ac",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCdB",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1207967093,
      "version": 6,
      "versionNonce": 1415779184,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "Bw94ZARaj5CggLfOt801m",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2481.6760718029414,
      "y": 7054.58425084392,
      "width": 1291.953085357232,
      "height": 53.80806814942388,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCdC",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1254562875,
      "version": 56,
      "versionNonce": 1704860560,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "内存泄漏相关概念\n- Memory overflow:内存溢出，没有足够的内存提供申请者使用。\n- Memory leak: 内存泄漏是指程序中己动态分配的堆内存由于某种原因程序未释放或无法释放，造成系统内存的浪费，导致程序运行速度减慢甚至系统崩溃等严重后果。内存泄漏的堆积终将导致内存溢出。",
      "fontSize": 14.348818173179703,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "内存泄漏相关概念\n- Memory overflow:内存溢出，没有足够的内存提供申请者使用。\n- Memory leak: 内存泄漏是指程序中己动态分配的堆内存由于某种原因程序未释放或无法释放，造成系统内存的浪费，导致程序运行速度减慢甚至系统崩溃等严重后果。内存泄漏的堆积终将导致内存溢出。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "fuLuaf7GXUUOXToqLJCxq",
      "type": "image",
      "x": -2703.3502461663743,
      "y": 7766.7741198246395,
      "width": 743,
      "height": 356,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "transparent",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCdD",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1016913877,
      "version": 310,
      "versionNonce": 1603216752,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "status": "saved",
      "fileId": "cf158040236ada093ea8b06fe3993b1716be7acd",
      "scale": [
        1,
        1
      ],
      "crop": null
    },
    {
      "id": "1i6bKSrPVxr23It5wCOc-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2139.6964606456777,
      "y": 7667.342353524278,
      "width": 782.7798461914062,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCdE",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2128920469,
      "version": 52,
      "versionNonce": 7612816,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "比较以上两种情况，我们就会发现，内存泄漏的发生跟ThreadLocalMap中的key是否使用\n弱引用是没有关系的。那么内存泄漏的的真正原因是什么呢？",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "比较以上两种情况，我们就会发现，内存泄漏的发生跟ThreadLocalMap中的key是否使用弱引用是没有关系的。那么内存泄漏的的真正原因是什么呢？",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "GVizqiZz2IGp0IuGrtcKR",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2001.753895200688,
      "y": 7731.11371976495,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCdF",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1584951355,
      "version": 28,
      "versionNonce": 258537328,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "细心的同学会发现，在以上两种内存泄漏的情况中，都有两个前提：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "细心的同学会发现，在以上两种内存泄漏的情况中，都有两个前提：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "oP_hJ_MJLzqNZRYpn6ijA",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1932.2760933760246,
      "y": 7583.990280345818,
      "width": 230.43992614746094,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCdG",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 934413557,
      "version": 83,
      "versionNonce": 827881360,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. 没有手动删除这个Entry",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. 没有手动删除这个Entry",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "KXyMqUmFBh0eXf01eijvj",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1928.1736109331125,
      "y": 7617.956527265239,
      "width": 638.3197631835938,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCdH",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1477751003,
      "version": 292,
      "versionNonce": 137922928,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. Thread依然运行，ThreadLocalMap一直存在，上一个任务已执行完成",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. Thread依然运行，ThreadLocalMap一直存在，上一个任务已执行完成",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "kxMvC74H3q10LMw-Zq0PU",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2048.8726499748027,
      "y": 7681.199749318019,
      "width": 928.5878135326525,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCdI",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 142492475,
      "version": 203,
      "versionNonce": 478348688,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "第一点很好理解，只要在使用完ThreadLocal，调用其remove方法删除对应的Entry，就能避免内存泄漏。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "第一点很好理解，只要在使用完ThreadLocal，调用其remove方法删除对应的Entry，就能避免内存泄漏。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "EJ7Xo9OcV7BqW8Zbtw8MJ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2023.3932381754887,
      "y": 7730.929434179074,
      "width": 781.6597900390625,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCdJ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2011619829,
      "version": 81,
      "versionNonce": 625335152,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "第二点稍微复杂一点， 由于ThreadLocalMap是Thread的一个属性，被当前线程所引用，\n所以它的生命周期跟Thread一样长。那么在使用完ThreadLocal的使用，如果当前Thread\n也随之执行结束，ThreadLocalMap自然也会被gc回收，从根源上避免了内存泄漏。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "第二点稍微复杂一点， 由于ThreadLocalMap是Thread的一个属性，被当前线程所引用，所以它的生命周期跟Thread一样长。那么在使用完ThreadLocal的使用，如果当前Thread也随之执行结束，ThreadLocalMap自然也会被gc回收，从根源上避免了内存泄漏。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "XbHRViaF1Y5nJ6Z0IcHxv",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2004.5884039347177,
      "y": 7826.361852304504,
      "width": 768.8597412109375,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCdK",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 132654043,
      "version": 79,
      "versionNonce": 522965904,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "综上，ThreadLocal内存泄漏的根源是：由于ThreadLocalMap的生命周期跟Thread一样\n长，如果没有手动删除对应key就会导致内存泄漏。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "综上，ThreadLocal内存泄漏的根源是：由于ThreadLocalMap的生命周期跟Thread一样长，如果没有手动删除对应key就会导致内存泄漏。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "DfZwo6Ca0RwmMI46r5pAt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1911.9687287416032,
      "y": 8121.042453782395,
      "width": 797.8798217773438,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCdL",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 927987381,
      "version": 38,
      "versionNonce": 416869744,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "根据刚才的分析, 我们知道了： 无论ThreadLocalMap中的key使用哪种类型引用都无法完全\n避免内存泄漏，跟使用弱引用没有关系。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "根据刚才的分析, 我们知道了： 无论ThreadLocalMap中的key使用哪种类型引用都无法完全避免内存泄漏，跟使用弱引用没有关系。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "IL3SKfM3NS63nn25QnyHt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2292.4115420504972,
      "y": 8183.702185933102,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCdM",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1972342133,
      "version": 131,
      "versionNonce": 797630864,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "相对第一种方式，第二种方式显然更不好控制，特别是使用线程池的时候，线程结束是不会\n销毁的。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "相对第一种方式，第二种方式显然更不好控制，特别是使用线程池的时候，线程结束是不会销毁的。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "gYfYKNtvhQKV3ayRQL82V",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1906.0612262425548,
      "y": 8319.1652143977,
      "width": 790.1998291015625,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCdN",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 387051611,
      "version": 54,
      "versionNonce": 205111152,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "也就是说，只要记得在使用完ThreadLocal及时的调用remove，无论key是强引用还是弱引\n用都不会有问题。那么为什么key要用弱引用呢？",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "也就是说，只要记得在使用完ThreadLocal及时的调用remove，无论key是强引用还是弱引用都不会有问题。那么为什么key要用弱引用呢？",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "BYIM0d0b9p7Yd1837eHfH",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1921.4822846272198,
      "y": 8141.501464461866,
      "width": 792.15966796875,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCdO",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 499723515,
      "version": 97,
      "versionNonce": 1020800912,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "这就意味着使用完ThreadLocal，CurrentThread依然运行的前提下，就算忘记调用remove\n方法，弱引用比强引用可以多一层保障：弱引用的ThreadLocal会被回收，对应的value在\n下一次ThreadLocalMap调用set,get,remove中的任一方法的时候会被清除，从而避免内存\n泄漏。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "这就意味着使用完ThreadLocal，CurrentThread依然运行的前提下，就算忘记调用remove方法，弱引用比强引用可以多一层保障：弱引用的ThreadLocal会被回收，对应的value在下一次ThreadLocalMap调用set,get,remove中的任一方法的时候会被清除，从而避免内存泄漏。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yg-ZNRZDZ06EBhCPk5epO",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1102.770780315223,
      "y": 6591.29796652421,
      "width": 787.019775390625,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCdP",
