      "seed": 1984720891,
      "version": 65,
      "versionNonce": 1034901392,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "我们可以通过ThreadLocal在同一线程，不同组件中传递公共变量",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "mN6hZU3aOVvcRkKNuwDwQ",
      "originalText": "我们可以通过ThreadLocal在同一线程，不同组件中传递公共变量",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "-aOFsCQyOlypKtspRSr1X",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1602.6894003648129,
      "y": 4464.551114398851,
      "width": 794.0596923828125,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCdn",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 708608667,
      "version": 70,
      "versionNonce": 960473456,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "synchronizedThreadLocal原理同步机制采用'以时间换空间'的方式, 只提供了一份变量,让不\n同的线程排队访问ThreadLocal采用'以空间换时间'的方式, 为每一个线程都提供了一份变量\n的副本,从而实现同时访问而相不干扰侧重点多个线程之间访问资源的同步多线程中让每个\n线程之间的数据相互隔离",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "synchronizedThreadLocal原理同步机制采用'以时间换空间'的方式, 只提供了一份变量,让不同的线程排队访问ThreadLocal采用'以空间换时间'的方式, 为每一个线程都提供了一份变量的副本,从而实现同时访问而相不干扰侧重点多个线程之间访问资源的同步多线程中让每个线程之间的数据相互隔离",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "hClG_H-NuuSca9Q0oOhmS",
