      "index": "cCer",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 135130587,
      "version": 140,
      "versionNonce": 1072642928,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634760,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "每次创建ThreadLocal时，nextHashCode递增0x61c88647，确保哈希码唯一\n// 示例：连续创建ThreadLocal时的哈希码\nThreadLocal A = new ThreadLocal(); // 哈希码：0\nThreadLocal B = new ThreadLocal(); // 哈希码：0x61c88647\nThreadLocal C = new ThreadLocal(); // 哈希码：0xc3910c94",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "4jcy2I1jZNgWWJ2HtvH65",
      "originalText": "每次创建ThreadLocal时，nextHashCode递增0x61c88647，确保哈希码唯一\n// 示例：连续创建ThreadLocal时的哈希码\nThreadLocal A = new ThreadLocal(); // 哈希码：0\nThreadLocal B = new ThreadLocal(); // 哈希码：0x61c88647\nThreadLocal C = new ThreadLocal(); // 哈希码：0xc3910c94",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
