      "text": "在多线程环境下，希望所有线程共享同一个ThreadLocal实例，应该将其定义为静态（static）",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "73rqW3aCFaLoOeLoZpxOg",
      "originalText": "在多线程环境下，希望所有线程共享同一个ThreadLocal实例，应该将其定义为静态（static）",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
