      "text": "当Thread销毁之后，对应的ThreadLocalMap也会随之销毁，能减少内存的使用。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "2OzcgEtBXVO0H6hj3v0I7",
      "originalText": "当Thread销毁之后，对应的ThreadLocalMap也会随之销毁，能减少内存的使用。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
