    {
      "id": "Au3rryMgrzbc8smiM30ys",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2008.0966890215368,
      "y": 6137.593604856399,
      "width": 975.2027451464564,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCof",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1708720629,
      "version": 244,
      "versionNonce": 1519033200,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CAS在、等实现上有非常广泛的应用。如下图所示，中，，。在AtomicInteger中提供的线程安全方法中，通过\n字段valueOffset的值可以定位到AtomicInteger对象中，从而可以根据CAS实现对value字段的原子操作。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CAS在、等实现上有非常广泛的应用。如下图所示，中，，。在AtomicInteger中提供的线程安全方法中，通过字段valueOffset的值可以定位到AtomicInteger对象中，从而可以根据CAS实现对value字段的原子操作。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "036HWNJJQAC86LCYueoLA",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2031.8616953325795,
      "y": 6432.509821532091,
      "width": 784.2197875976562,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCog",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 208257269,
      "version": 69,
      "versionNonce": 1569919888,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "下图为某个自增操作前后的内存示意图，，通过得到；然后通过CAS进行原子性的更新操\n作，成功则返回，否则继续重试，直到更新成功为止。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "下图为某个自增操作前后的内存示意图，，通过得到；然后通过CAS进行原子性的更新操作，成功则返回，否则继续重试，直到更新成功为止。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Cg_wde3YxC-SppbSVX_6E",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1930.680842736947,
      "y": 7289.204625222309,
      "width": 797.9193115234375,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCoh",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1407804597,
      "version": 49,
      "versionNonce": 1199943024,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "不管是 Hotspot 中的 Atomic::cmpxchg 方法，还是 Java 中的 compareAndSwapInt 方法，\n它们。CAS 指令作为一种硬件原语，有着天然的原子性，这也正是 CAS 的价值所在。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "不管是 Hotspot 中的 Atomic::cmpxchg 方法，还是 Java 中的 compareAndSwapInt 方法，它们。CAS 指令作为一种硬件原语，有着天然的原子性，这也正是 CAS 的价值所在。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "rsqs8PMwYYcSB4DXlwX6x",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1990.1366971130758,
      "y": 7538.950466536891,
      "width": 745.2599487304688,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCoi",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 884618107,
      "version": 157,
      "versionNonce": 520757648,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CAS 虽然高效地解决了原子操作，但是还是存在一些缺陷的，主要表现在三个方面：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CAS 虽然高效地解决了原子操作，但是还是存在一些缺陷的，主要表现在三个方面：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
