      "seed": 610375195,
      "version": 60,
      "versionNonce": 402324880,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ABA问题及其解决方案",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ABA问题及其解决方案",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p79aNOIOCsYbwbdfQhegS",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1858.336674709805,
      "y": 8048.605886778699,
      "width": 780.0399780273438,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCon",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2092870933,
      "version": 60,
      "versionNonce": 929653616,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CAS算法实现一个重要前提需要取出内存中某时刻的数据，而在下时刻比较并替换，那么\n在这个时间差类会导致数据的变化。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CAS算法实现一个重要前提需要取出内存中某时刻的数据，而在下时刻比较并替换，那么在这个时间差类会导致数据的变化。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "EiVZP9S9v9jNQvy1n7VMD",
      "type": "text",
