      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "什么是ABA问题",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "什么是ABA问题",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "tTYoQLKak1e4-oViQXAE9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1845.8117726945252,
      "y": 8140.3275949244035,
      "width": 766.7920534854325,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCop",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 250757749,
      "version": 115,
      "versionNonce": 759919984,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "当有多个线程对一个原子类进行操作的时候，某个线程在短时间内将原子类的值A修改\n为B，又马上将其修改为A，此时其他线程不感知，还是会修改成功。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "当有多个线程对一个原子类进行操作的时候，某个线程在短时间内将原子类的值A修改为B，又马上将其修改为A，此时其他线程不感知，还是会修改成功。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
