      "text": "ABA问题的解决方案",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "Rvukb4CGj_eH-DTjHQN1r",
      "originalText": "ABA问题的解决方案",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "13wbI9o6Kyy1BpYSM2hNP",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1868.8137531639668,
      "y": 8037.6181251443795,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCos",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1041984187,
      "version": 162,
      "versionNonce": 649275280,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "数据库有个锁称为乐观锁，是一种基于数据版本实现数据同步的机制，每次修改一次数据，\n版本就会进行累加。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "数据库有个锁称为乐观锁，是一种基于数据版本实现数据同步的机制，每次修改一次数据，版本就会进行累加。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "C5z68ccEmrBiMnr1JSwdT",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -1579.0625811147752,
