      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Java也提供了相应的原子引用类，添加版本记录",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "C5z68ccEmrBiMnr1JSwdT",
      "originalText": "Java也提供了相应的原子引用类，添加版本记录",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "8CX-fFLBU06FDbgWPeay6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1833.5466077389376,
      "y": 8496.480520373152,
      "width": 784.4197998046875,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCov",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 317650171,
      "version": 86,
      "versionNonce": 1789143920,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "，。这样就可以保证每次修改后的版本也会往上递增。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "，。这样就可以保证每次修改后的版本也会往上递增。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
