    {
      "id": "9DBrWfi0ZzjF4PPK2CchP",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1857.272932342335,
      "y": 8872.849707457748,
      "width": 697.0634634418315,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCox",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 547577787,
      "version": 110,
      "versionNonce": 1038957936,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "AtomicStampedReference的get方法设计为传入int[]数组而非单独int变量，主\n要是为了‌避免参数被编译器优化‌，确保时间戳的‌可见性‌和‌原子性‌。具体机制如\n下：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "AtomicStampedReference的get方法设计为传入int[]数组而非单独int变量，主要是为了‌避免参数被编译器优化‌，确保时间戳的‌可见性‌和‌原子性‌。具体机制如下：",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "I2IPEU8oMg19NxJzo1H86",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1833.9917984425665,
      "y": 8950.168690812454,
      "width": 140,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCoy",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 898616693,
      "version": 116,
      "versionNonce": 1352896912,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "‌避免编译器优化‌",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "‌避免编译器优化‌",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "bXIKZ6Uf3yOos65nlCt62",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1844.9994785371857,
      "y": 8986.431518012163,
      "width": 709.8228034420273,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCoz",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 104181851,
      "version": 124,
      "versionNonce": 709103472,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Java编译器可能对局部变量进行优化（如逃逸分析），导致时间戳值在多线程环\n境中的不可见性。通过数组参数，编译器无法优化数组元素的存储位置，确保时\n间戳值在不同线程中的可见性",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Java编译器可能对局部变量进行优化（如逃逸分析），导致时间戳值在多线程环境中的不可见性。通过数组参数，编译器无法优化数组元素的存储位置，确保时间戳值在不同线程中的可见性",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "dJz8vmPba6S3vFKJ6Shse",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1690.6025788964848,
      "y": 9678.188109717472,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
