      "versionNonce": 1710779792,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "‌数组参数的内存语义‌",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "‌数组参数的内存语义‌",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "9aI8dnNOUGJekIw7pQWOq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1804.2664400183758,
      "y": 9132.93850074773,
      "width": 797.9999389648438,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCp3",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1569617819,
      "version": 118,
      "versionNonce": 1715139440,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "数组元素在Java内存模型中被视为‌堆内存‌，具有更强的可见性保证。而局部变量可能被优化\n为‌栈内存‌，在多线程场景中可能导致数据竞争",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "数组元素在Java内存模型中被视为‌堆内存‌，具有更强的可见性保证。而局部变量可能被优化为‌栈内存‌，在多线程场景中可能导致数据竞争",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "WmTGLYjJK25L_bOUSfzwz",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1654.2418934392463,
      "y": 9830.611633801194,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
