    },
    {
      "id": "BXk231JfbmuNqW2AmZ6l7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2153.0442005681525,
      "y": 15099.40795857526,
      "width": 789.419677734375,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCpa",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 811750325,
      "version": 22,
      "versionNonce": 1610816400,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "上述方法调用了Unsafe类的getAndAddLong方法，该方法内部是个native方法，它的逻辑\n是采用自旋的方式不断更新目标值，直到更新成功。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "上述方法调用了Unsafe类的getAndAddLong方法，该方法内部是个native方法，它的逻辑是采用自旋的方式不断更新目标值，直到更新成功。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "lU7hK2o6H07Kj5zEp8Vna",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2158.334361700965,
      "y": 15146.90795857526,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCpb",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1013296667,
      "version": 22,
      "versionNonce": 1778001264,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "在并发量较低的环境下，线程冲突的概率比较小，自旋的次数不会很多。但是，高并发环境\n下，N个线程同时进行自旋操作，会出现大量失败并不断自旋的情况，此时AtomicLong的\n自旋会成为瓶颈。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "在并发量较低的环境下，线程冲突的概率比较小，自旋的次数不会很多。但是，高并发环境下，N个线程同时进行自旋操作，会出现大量失败并不断自旋的情况，此时AtomicLong的自旋会成为瓶颈。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "n1aR_Z6Ju0JjEo7OcNxjc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2157.66419568534,
      "y": 15244.40795857526,
      "width": 798.65966796875,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCpc",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1755845909,
      "version": 22,
      "versionNonce": 1715022224,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "这就是LongAdder引入的初衷——解决高并发环境下AtomicInteger，AtomicLong的自旋瓶\n颈问题。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "这就是LongAdder引入的初衷——解决高并发环境下AtomicInteger，AtomicLong的自旋瓶颈问题。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
