      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCph",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 92591477,
      "version": 27,
      "versionNonce": 596695920,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "低并发、一般的业务场景下AtomicLong是足够了。如果并发量很多，存在大量写多读少的\n情况，那LongAdder可能更合适。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "低并发、一般的业务场景下AtomicLong是足够了。如果并发量很多，存在大量写多读少的情况，那LongAdder可能更合适。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "P-Ci2h3jBvEbJxCnlu7wC",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1763.9943119573127,
