      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCqJ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 536413499,
      "version": 13,
      "versionNonce": 1817342320,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "只有从未出现过并发冲突的时候，base基数才会使用到，一旦出现了并发冲突，之后所有\n的操作都只针对Cell[]数组中的单元Cell。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "只有从未出现过并发冲突的时候，base基数才会使用到，一旦出现了并发冲突，之后所有的操作都只针对Cell[]数组中的单元Cell。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "u3se06dA1iUPhV2hy_U0D",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2015.424205450965,
      "y": 20133.574498005873,
      "width": 794.1796875,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCqK",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1005666293,
      "version": 13,
      "versionNonce": 224107920,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "如果Cell[]数组未初始化，会调用父类的longAccumelate去初始化Cell[]，如果Cell[]已经初\n始化但是冲突发生在Cell单元内，则也调用父类的longAccumelate，此时可能就需要对\nCell[]扩容了。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "如果Cell[]数组未初始化，会调用父类的longAccumelate去初始化Cell[]，如果Cell[]已经初始化但是冲突发生在Cell单元内，则也调用父类的longAccumelate，此时可能就需要对Cell[]扩容了。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "9Ocbr7NgvZXMaiZJHkmRe",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2009.01429334159,
      "y": 20231.074498005873,
      "width": 781.35986328125,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCqL",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 649766363,
      "version": 13,
      "versionNonce": 1038271344,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "这也是LongAdder设计的精妙之处：尽量减少热点冲突，不到最后万不得已，尽量将CAS\n操作延迟。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "这也是LongAdder设计的精妙之处：尽量减少热点冲突，不到最后万不得已，尽量将CAS操作延迟。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
