      "seed": 865317941,
      "version": 24,
      "versionNonce": 1951909776,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "返回累加的和，也就是\"当前时刻\"的计数值",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "返回累加的和，也就是\"当前时刻\"的计数值",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "xggwMFWkQVebx6AhNDtjU",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2068.0644642400275,
      "y": 22093.574418533004,
      "width": 719.4599609375,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCqR",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1205376411,
      "version": 24,
      "versionNonce": 1939224944,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "* 注意： 高并发时，除非全局加锁，否则得不到程序运行中某个时刻绝对准确的值",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "* 注意： 高并发时，除非全局加锁，否则得不到程序运行中某个时刻绝对准确的值",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Gnm6U6V9q-L3mPYrKALKK",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2098.0644642400275,
      "y": 22116.074418533004,
      "width": 779.4599609375,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCqS",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 802776469,
      "version": 24,
      "versionNonce": 1662539152,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "*  此返回值可能不是绝对准确的，因为调用这个方法时还有其他线程可能正在进行计数累\n加,",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "*  此返回值可能不是绝对准确的，因为调用这个方法时还有其他线程可能正在进行计数累加,",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yBw7bkHeWPAqNbhAlTHI8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2108.0644642400275,
      "y": 22176.074418533004,
      "width": 799.4599609375,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCqT",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1627990587,
      "version": 24,
      "versionNonce": 963480432,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "*  方法的返回时刻和调用时刻不是同一个点，在有并发的情况下，这个值只是近似准确的计\n数值",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "*  方法的返回时刻和调用时刻不是同一个点，在有并发的情况下，这个值只是近似准确的计数值",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "rHxTM7soaqMCIFDckisxN",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1969.09095349784,
      "y": 22305.240922439254,
      "width": 798.179931640625,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cCqU",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2116983963,
      "version": 5,
      "versionNonce": 110568336,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772800634761,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "由于计算总和时没有对Cell数组进行加锁，所以在累加过程中可能有其他线程对Cell中的值\n进行了修改，也有可能对数组进行了扩容，所以sum返回的值并不是非常精确的，其返回值\n并不是一个调用sum方法时的原子快照值。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "由于计算总和时没有对Cell数组进行加锁，所以在累加过程中可能有其他线程对Cell中的值进行了修改，也有可能对数组进行了扩容，所以sum返回的值并不是非常精确的，其返回值并不是一个调用sum方法时的原子快照值。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
